reviews.text: Fast food quality dishes, but at a price slightly higher than fast-food shops. Good for a quick meal, not difficult to get a seat.

Comfortable place if you come at nonpeak hours. Afternoon tea and lunch sets are attractive. Prices are very competitive while quality is great. Recommended highly. Service fast and warm. Not crowded in the afternoon, can sit and talk with friends for over an hour.
Typical買得起的deluxe cafe. Especially the kid meal set which is even provide the good experience about enjoying the food.
Good choice, food taste ok, soup seemed a bit salty.
Nice staff

reviews.text: 弄到我的妹妹肚子痛😣
今晚在此食飯,杂排中的豬排和魚柳鹹到入唔到口。食物買相就不錯。
食物幾好，賣相有用心做出黎，服務員態度細心，價錢合理，整體 good
香草天使面十分清香丶唔配台式肉燥更加好食，份量比起其他餐廳多；雞扒外脆內嫩丶即叫即煎。
早餐員工未在狀態 午市可以 大衆化價錢
